1:24:09.792 --> 1:24:13.930
All right, Ed,
you can take me in.

1:24:14.063 --> 1:24:16.131
It's okay, Sam.

1:24:16.264 --> 1:24:18.635
Maybe you had
a good reason for speeding,

1:24:18.768 --> 1:24:20.937
even in the eyes of the law.

1:24:21.070 --> 1:24:24.306
