what she wanted?

1:24:24.439 --> 1:24:27.175
More than you'll ever know.

1:24:27.309 --> 1:24:28.711
Thank you.

1:24:31.948 --> 1:24:34.216
Eddie, are you seeing this?

1:24:34.349 --> 1:24:36.385
It was one of the strongest
storms of the year,

1:24:36.518 --> 1:24:39.454
yet none of the people
who went up there are wet.

1:25:45.621 --> 1:25:47.757
I'm so sorry.

1:25:49.558 --> 1:25:55.765
I know... nothing we can say
will bring you comfort...

1:25:55.898 --> 1:25:59.702
but we all know
where Sara is now.

1:25:59.836 --> 1:26:03.338
Safe in God's hands.

1:26:07.242 --> 1:26:10.213
Dad...

1:26:18.253 --> 1:26:20.823
Dad, I'm sorry
for what I said at the lake.

1:26:20.957 --> 1:26:22.290
I know how much you loved her,

1:26:22.424 --> 1:26:25.161
and you were just trying
to fulfil her wish.

1:26:25.293 --> 1:26:26.394
And, and you knew something

1:26:26.528 --> 1:26:28.097
that none of us
could understand,

1:26:28.231 --> 1:26:30.398
so I... thank you
for doing that for her.

1:26:38.107 --> 1:26:40.575
Dad.

1:26:55.258 --> 1:26:56.759
Must've been
the last picture she drew.

1:26:56.893 --> 1:27:00.562
I... I think she knew
God was coming for her.

1:27:00.696 --> 1:27:04.167
That's beautiful.

1:27:04.299 --> 1:27:07.435
I'll have it framed
and hung up in church.

1:27:11.573 --> 1:27:15.244
Danny...
Danny, look at this...

1:27:17.579 --> 1:27:20.149
Mom! Dad!

1:27:22.317 --> 1:27:24.720
<i>This</i> is
the last picture she drew.

1:27:24.854 --> 1:27:26.022
She's coming back!

1:27:26.155 --> 1:27:29.659
That means that, maybe...

1:27:32.460 --> 1:27:34.030
God...

1:27:34.163 --> 1:27:37.200
...are You gonna
let Sara come back to us?

1:27:37.332 --> 1:27:39.669
- Oh, Danny...
- Can You?

1:27:39.802 --> 1:27:41.737
- Will You, will You, please...
- Danny...

1:27:41.871 --> 1:27:43.572
Please, let Sara
come back to us?

1:27:43.706 --> 1:27:46.742
- Sweetheart, I'm sorry...
- Please, God.

1:27:46.876 --> 1:27:49.645
- Will You, please?
- You got to let her go.

1:27:49.779 --> 1:27:51.814
- Sara, please?
- I'm sorry, darling...

1:27:51.948 --> 1:27:53.783
- Please, Sara, please...
- I'm sorry...

1:27:53.916 --> 1:27:55.618
I'm so sorry, sweetie.

1:27:58.921 --> 1:28:01.456
Sara? Sara!

1:28:01.591 --> 1:28:03.025
Oh, my...

1:28:03.159 --> 1:28:05.628
- Oh!
- Sara! Sara...

1:28:05.761 --> 1:28:07.864
Oh...

1:28:07.997 --> 1:28:10.333
- Sara?
- Hi, Mommy...

1:28:10.465 --> 1:28:11.968
Daddy...

1:28:13.102 --> 1:28:14.136
Sara!

1:28:14.270 --> 1:28:15.304
Honey, how are you?

1:28:19.474 --> 1:28:22.712
It's a miracle!

1:28:22.845 --> 1:28:27.016
I told God that I didn't think
I was ready to go to Heaven

1:28:27.149 --> 1:28:29.517
and He told me to come back here
and take care of you.

1:28:29.652 --> 1:28:34.290
Oh, my... my baby...

1:28:34.422 --> 1:28:37.425
Oh, my baby, you're alive.

1:28:37.559 --> 1:28:39.595
You're alive.

1:28:39.729 --> 1:28:40.963
I love you so much.

1:28:42.832 --> 1:28:47.502
Thank You, God, thank You, God.

1:28:47.637 --> 1:28:48.470
Thank You, God.

1:28:48.604 --> 1:28:50.339
It, it, it's not possible.

1:28:50.472 --> 1:28:54.343
She wasn't breathing, there was
no, there was no pulse.

1:28:54.476 --> 1:28:56.746
You're beginning to catch on.

1:29:10.159 --> 1:29:11.761
It's a miracle!

1:29:23.306 --> 1:29:26.943
No, don't kneel.

1:29:27.076 --> 1:29:31.948
I'm just a... lucky girl
who God decided to visit.

1:29:32.081 --> 1:29:35.985
It... could've been
any one of you.

1:29:36.118 --> 1:29:39.355
He still may come back
to see one of you,

1:29:39.487 --> 1:29:41.791
just like He did with me.

1:29:47.797 --> 1:29:51.867
Please, get up...

1:29:52.001 --> 1:29:57.773
and... now you all
need to believe something.

1:29:59.642 --> 1:30:01.844
I can't cure anyone anymore.

1:30:01.978 --> 1:30:04.647
But... I wasn't the one

1:30:04.780 --> 1:30:07.984
who really cured people
in the first place.

1:30:08.117 --> 1:30:10.319
It was God.

1:30:10.453 --> 1:30:14.657
He just told me what to do
and... I did it.

1:30:14.790 --> 1:30:15.925
The truth is...

1:30:16.058 --> 1:30:18.327
all of you can cure people.

1:30:18.461 --> 1:30:21.330
You really can.

1:30:21.464 --> 1:30:25.401
All you have to do is
believe in God and pray to Him,

1:30:25.533 --> 1:30:28.371
and He'll help you.

1:30:28.536 --> 1:30:31.974
Sometimes...
we can't see it right away.

1:30:32.108 --> 1:30:34.877
Or sometimes the answer

1:30:35.011 --> 1:30:37.079
isn't exactly
what you've prayed for, but...

1:30:37.213 --> 1:30:39.415
He's listening.

1:30:39.547 --> 1:30:44.186
And soon you'll see how kind
and how wonderful He is.

1:30:44.320 --> 1:30:46.521
He's the best.

1:30:49.658 --> 1:30:52.328
He told me to tell you...

1:30:52.461 --> 1:30:58.401
to... love your children
and your families,

1:30:58.533 --> 1:31:02.204
and to try to help one another
every day.

1:31:04.539 --> 1:31:07.977
So...
when you all go home tonight...

1:31:08.110 --> 1:31:10.880
say a prayer
and ask what you can do

1:31:11.013 --> 1:31:15.418
to make your family strong
and to help other people.

1:31:15.550 --> 1:31:18.687
God <i>will</i> help you, because...

1:31:18.821 --> 1:31:22.391
well...

1:31:22.525 --> 1:31:25.194
He loves you all...

1:31:25.327 --> 1:31:27.296
a lot.

1:31:42.244 --> 1:31:44.447
...and, well, the expression,
"God works in mysterious ways"

1:31:44.579 --> 1:31:46.248
certainly rung true
in our community

1:31:46.382 --> 1:31:48.317
over the last week or so.

1:31:48.451 --> 1:31:50.986
As a matter of fact, on that
country road the other night,

1:31:51.120 --> 1:31:53.923
I was certain <i>I</i> was gonna meet
my maker... several times.

1:31:57.726 --> 1:32:00.262
For all of us, each in our own,
different way,

1:32:00.396 --> 1:32:04.800
I think God has opened a door,
has shown us a little light,

1:32:04.934 --> 1:32:08.037
has shown us that His arms were
around us, around our friends,

1:32:08.170 --> 1:32:10.873
our family, both in this life
and in the next one.

1:32:11.006 --> 1:32:13.909
Can you feel Jesse with us?

1:32:14.043 --> 1:32:17.079
You know, uh... I can.

1:32:20.116 --> 1:32:25.087
So, some of us who have been
witness to... modern miracles

1:32:25.221 --> 1:32:29.191
can get a small taste of what
it was like to be an apostle.

1:32:29.325 --> 1:32:32.862
For in their presence was
the one continuing miracle,

1:32:32.995 --> 1:32:34.663
the miracle
that we can all choose

1:32:34.797 --> 1:32:38.267
