through our lives...

1:32:38.400 --> 1:32:40.169
the presence of God.

1:32:56.519 --> 1:32:57.653
See, Daddy?

1:32:57.786 --> 1:32:59.421
It's like Jesus said.

1:32:59.555 --> 1:33:05.161
Faith as small as a mustard seed
can grow and spread,

1:33:05.294 --> 1:33:08.598
